flowchart TD
    A[User opens Collection screen] --> B{Search query\ngreater than or equal to 2 chars?}
    B -->|Yes| C[FTS5 full-text search]
    B -->|No| D[watchAll with SQL params]

    D --> E[SQL WHERE deleted = 0]
    D --> F[SQL WHERE media_type = ?]
    D --> G[SQL ORDER BY sort_column]

    E --> H[(SQLite with indexes)]
    F --> H
    G --> H
    C --> H

    H --> I[Stream of MediaItem rows]
    I --> J{lentOnly or\nrippedOnly?}
    J -->|Yes| K[In-memory filter\nvia loan/rip IDs]
    J -->|No| L[Pass through]
    K --> M[CollectionProvider emits filtered list]
    L --> M

    M --> N{Grid or Table view?}
    N -->|Grid| O[GridView.builder — lazy]
    N -->|Table| P[PaginatedDataTable2 — 50 rows/page]

    style H fill:#e1f5fe
    style M fill:#f3e5f5
